line_1: To quarrel at a few mistakes,
line_2: Are these the ways your wisdom take,

line_1: To quarrel at a few mistakes,
line_2: Whilst France their own advantage makes,

line_1: And then for mine obligingly mistakes
line_2: The first Lampoon Sir Will. or Bubo makes.

line_1: Atone for each impostor's wild mistakes,
line_2: And mend the blunders pride or folly makes?

line_1: Learn well his lesson, and ne'er fear mistakes;
